703
01:19:26,480 --> 01:19:28,277
Yeah.

704
01:19:29,400 --> 01:19:32,039
Well, it's beautiful country.

705
01:19:32,160 --> 01:19:34,116
And I could see having
some kind of a...

706
01:19:35,800 --> 01:19:37,631
you know, vacation place, retreat.

707
